title: Conair Instant Heat Compact Hot Rollers
description: The Conair Instant Heat Compact Hot Rollers give you flawless curls on the go. This dual-voltage hot roller set includes 10 multi-size rollers (4 Small, 3 Medium and 3 Large) and clips for a variety of styles. It features a patented roller design with starter strip for quick, easy setting and 90-second heat-up feature for instant results. The soft handy pouch makes it easy to carry in gym bag, backpack or suitcase.
